latestPosts.caption:
I recently went bald and my experience has been quite something. As women, we often set limitations in life, go by the rules and even keep ourselves caged. With this transformation, I have set myself free, free from limitations and intending to break the beauty standards that the world has set upon us and I do it with a lot of courage and faith in my heart!
Today, I also carry the memory of my late husband close, in his blazer that still holds his warmth. ♥️

Sending power and love to all the women out there! ✨

. 📸- @portraitsatplaces 

#ShanthiPriya #BaldAndBeautiful

Monday magic… straight from the golden 90s ✨
30 years ago, “Chori Chori Dil Tera” touched hearts… and today, sung by @kumarsanuofficial Ji & #sujatagoswamy Ji. It’s still doing the same.
Back then, it was in the Top 10… today, it’s trending once again — and all thanks to your love.
From the sets of Phool Aur Angaar with the amazing @mithunchakrabortyofficial ji, to now recreating this moment after decades — it’s truly magical.
My heart is full. ♥️
